ched with physically reasonable matter\nwithin GR and that true black hole mimickers require either exotic matter or\nbeyond-GR effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Jan 2022 19:08:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Jul 2022 11:44:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-17"}
