 certain parameters. Thereby, we expand on a\ncorresponding result for quadratically growing $-g$ proved by Lankeit and\nLankeit (Nonlinearity, 32(5):1569--1596, 2019).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Feb 2022 10:30:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-02"}
